AB  - This paper extends existing tables of bounds on critical values of the Durbin-Watson test for regressions with an intercept and regressions with an intercept plus a linear trend. It also presents tables of bounds for regressions with a full set of monthly seasonal dummy variables, both with and without a linear trend regressor.
